firefox-nightly.pl (120204)

Firefox Nightly/Aurora install & update script for Slackware Linux.

This will download and update to/install the latest version of Firefox
Nightly/Aurora. The script must be run as root (or sudo).

By default the script is set to Nightly x86_64, you can change to Aurora
and/or i686 by following the comments in the script. 

Usage: sudo perl firefox-nightly.pl